title: Richkids Of Beverly Hills S02E01 Richkids Return WEB-DL x264-RKS
description: EJ gets all the #RichKids back together for a day of yachting with one notable exception: Dorothy's serious boyfriend Cooper is a no-show. Is he purposely missing all group get-togethers? Then, Dorothy surprises her clique with nvitations to join her for a 10-day trip to China, and Cooper is already showing reservations. Meanwhile, Morgan is getting tired of her workaholic man Brendan. See them duke it out about spending more time together. Finally, Roxy finds herself in an online relationship.Is she ready to open up to love?
